
'''Eugenie Musayidire,''' yavutse  Ku ya 25 Ukuboza  1952 , mu [[Rwanda]],Numunyarwandakazi uharanira  uburenganzira  bwa muntu uba mu [[Ubudage|Budage]]  . Yahawe igihembo mpuzamahanga cya Nuremberg mu burenganzira  bwa muntu mu 2007.

== Ubuzima Bwite ==
Eugénie Musayidire ni [[Abatutsi|Umwe mubatutsi]] bake mu Rwanda. Yahunze mu 1973, igihe yaburiwe ko yenda gufatwa. Yabanje guhungira mu [[Uburundi|Burundi]], akomeza amasomo ye muri kaminuza y’Uburundi mu bijyanye n’ubukungu n’imibereho . Mu 1977, yasabye ubuhungiro muri politiki mu [[Ubudage|Budage]], kandi yitoza kuba umufasha wa farumasi . Yareze umuryango atura i Siegburg, aho yakoraga mw'Itorero ry'Abaluteriyani  <ref name="N">Présentation de la lauréate du prix des droits de l'homme de la ville de Nuremberg Eugénie Musayidire, sur www.nuernberg.de </ref> Yaje gukora i Bonn.

Yize ko umuryango we wishwe mu gihe cya [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|Genoside yakorewe abatutsi mu Rwanda mu 1994]] . : abura nyina, murumuna we na bene wabo benshi kandi baziranye. Inshuti yamuzaniye ibuye, vestige yonyine murugo rwumuryango we. Yasobanuye ibisobanuro by'aya makuba yandika igitabo cyitwa ''Ma pierre qui parle'', mu 1999 <ref name="Buch">[http://www.imbuto.net/uploads/buchbesprechungen/07_mein_stein_spricht.pdf Critique de livre] sur imbuto.net consulté le 18. </ref> .

Eugénie Musayidire yiyemeje mu buryo bw'intangarugero mu bwiyunge hagati y'Abahutu n'Abatutsi mu Rwanda. Mu 2001, yasuye igihugu akomokamo, ku nshuro ya mbere kuva yava mu buhungiro. Muri uwo mwaka, yashinze mu Budage ishyirahamwe  " Hoffnung  muri Ruanda e. v. »(« Ibyiringiro  mu Rwanda "). Abikesheje  inkunga  y'Itorero  ry'Abaporotesitanti   b'Abadage , yashinze, mu 2003, i Nyanza, Ikigo gishinzwe kuvura urubyiruko, ''IZERE'' , aho abana ndetse n'urubyiruko bahura n'ingaruka  za Genoside bitaweho.

Muri uku kuguma mu Rwanda mu 2001, yashoboye guhura  n'umwicanyi wo mu muryango we, wahoze aturanye. Iyi nama nicyifuzo cyo kwiyunga  byatumye havuka firime, ''Mama wa Assassin'' . Iyi filime  yahawe igihembo cya Adolf-Grimme .

Kuwa 30 Nzeri  2007 , Eugénie Musayidire ahabwa igihembo mpuzamahanga cy’uburenganzira bwa muntu cya Nuremberg, gitangwa na Doudou Diène wahoze ari umunyamabanga [[Umuryango w’Abibumye|w’umuryango w’abibumbye]] ku bibazo by’ivanguramoko, ivangura rishingiye ku moko, abanyamahanga no kutoroherana <ref>[https://www.nuernberg.de/internet/menschenrechte/preisverleihung_2007.html] Cérémonie de remise des prix 2007 des droits de l'homme de la Ville de [[Nuremberg]], sur www.nuernberg.de.</ref> .

Muri Gicurasi 2015, documentaire  yitwa ''Mein Stein spricht'' ( ''Ibuye ryanjye rivuga : inzira ndende yo kwiyunga mu Rwanda'' ), ku nkuru ya Eugénie Musayidire  ivugwa kuri televiziyo ARD-alpha <ref>[https://programm.ard.de/TV/Themenschwerpunkte/Dokus--Reportagen/Alle-Dokumentationen/Startseite/?sendung=2848714585036103 Documentaire ''Ma Pierre parle''], ARD-alpha.</ref>

